               <p>Mr. Barnes. I am a broker, and live in Pope's Head Alley. I transact business for the Rev. 
               <persName id="t17690405-48-person474">
                  Hugh 
                  Lewis 
               <interp inst="t17690405-48-person474" type="surname" value="Lewis"></interp>
